		<p class="text-[var(--muted)] mb-4">Last updated: February 2026</p>

		<div class="prose text-[var(--muted)] space-y-4">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mt-6 mb-3">Our approach</h2>
			<p class="text-[var(--muted)] mb-4">We keep things simple. This website does not use tracking cookies.</p>
			<p class="text-[var(--muted)]">We use Plausible Analytics to see how people use the site. Plausible is privacy-focused and doesn't use cookies or collect personal dataâ€”so no cookie consent banner needed.</p>

